Miss Lin,

64
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:51,920
All these things brought in are rare treasures.

65
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:54,600
Why cry over such an ugly sachet?

66
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:59,160
Nanling and Beiyue are at war right now.

67
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:01,760
