69
00:06:03,760 --> 00:06:04,480
You see,

70
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:07,200
shouldn't you show some appreciation?

71
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,480
Since the City Lord is busy with official duties,

72
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,360
we should prioritize important matters.

73
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:19,200
I've been making a sachet lately.

74
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:21,000
It has the effect of refreshing the mind.

75
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,200
Once I finish it,

76
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:24,760
I'll deliver it to the City Lord myself.

77
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,440
Alright.

78
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,320
Then I'll be waiting for you.

79
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,320
Okay.

80
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:30,640
Chief Hong,

81
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:32,240
let's go.

82
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:33,520
