83
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:51,680
Miss,

84
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,200
why go to such trouble?

85
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:54,880
No matter what,

86
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:57,680
