98
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:24,440
Deputy General Lu has held the front line for two days and nights.

99
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:26,440
I'm afraid he can't hold out much longer.

100
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:27,200
What did you say?

101
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:28,520
Who says I can't hold out?

102
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,080
I never thought

103
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:01,760
I would meet you here.

104
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:05,080
As a man of Nanling,

105
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:07,440
it's my duty to defend my homeland without hesitation.

106
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:11,880
Alright.

107
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,320
From now on, we will

108
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,000
fight side by side.

109
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:26,880
Miss

110
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,680
