111
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,120
She's doing very well.

112
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,760
She's about to become

113
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:39,000
the wife of the city lord.

114
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:43,200
She has finally fulfilled her wish.

115
00:08:48,680 --> 00:08:49,440
Do your best.

116
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:50,960
Together,

117
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:52,240
let's return alive.

118
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:54,760
It's a promise.

119
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,880
Tomorrow is the big day.

120
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,400
Everyone, stay spirited.

121
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,800
Make sure everything is in order.

122
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:19,880
Don't let the Lin family lose face in front of the city lord.

123
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,800
This wedding dress fits so well.

124
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,440
And Miss is so beautiful.

125
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,000
You will surely be

126
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,560
the most beautiful city lord's wife in Nanling.

127
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:40,520
Miss,

128
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:44,560
Miss,

129
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:46,560
The big day is almost here.

130
00:09:46,640 --> 00:09:47,880
You should be a little happier.

131
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:20,520
Miss, look quickly.

132
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,680
The Madam has given you the bracelet from her youth.

133
00:10:22,680 --> 00:10:23,760
She has bestowed it upon you.

134
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:25,440
She said it's a wedding gift for you.

135
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:37,120
It shows that the Lord must have spoken well of you to the Madam.

136
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:38,800
He must have praised you a lot.

137
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:40,640
That's why the Madam is so fond of you.

138
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,400
If you like it,

139
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:45,400
just take it.

140
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,560
Miss.

141
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:21,760
Please forgive me, Miss.

142
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:24,120
Li Yan

143
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:44,760
I inherit the mandate of heaven and continue the grand legacy.

144
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:47,760
The way to govern a nation begins with managing the family.

145
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:50,880
The relationship between husband and wife reflects the order of heaven and earth.

146
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:53,200
It is truly with reverence for the ancestral rites.

147
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:54,760
And with sincere devotion to mutual support.

148
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,440
This is of utmost importance.

149
00:11:57,640 --> 00:12:00,000
Lin Qianjin, daughter of the Minister of State,

150
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,560
possesses the virtue of chastity and calmness.

151
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:04,200
She is worthy to be a model of womanhood.

152
00:12:04,760 --> 00:12:07,120
She should join in upholding the ancestral temples and the will of heaven and earth.

153
00:12:07,640 --> 00:12:10,560
Hereby, she is appointed as the Lady of the City Lord.

154
00:12:13,560 --> 00:12:17,120
Bestow upon her the fragrance of a hundred washes of moon branches.

155
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,240
Stop right there.

156
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:40,760
Move aside.

157
00:12:45,760 --> 00:12:46,320
Wait.

158
00:12:48,520 --> 00:12:49,120
Changle

159
00:12:49,560 --> 00:12:50,440
Do not make a scene.

160
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:51,760
What is it?

161
00:12:51,760 --> 00:12:53,320
Wait until the investiture ceremony is over to talk.

162
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:54,240
No.

163
00:12:54,760 --> 00:12:56,880
There are things I must say right now.

164
00:12:57,560 --> 00:12:58,560
Lin Qianjin

165
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:01,000
This morning, news of battle came from the border.

166
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:03,440
Li Yan was assassinated.

167
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,760
He is gravely injured and unconscious.

168
00:13:05,560 --> 00:13:08,000
The reinforcements he led are surrounded by Northern Yue soldiers.

169
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:11,120
Perhaps, after this ceremony ends,

170
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:12,320
in this world,

171
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:14,440
there will be no more Li Yan.

172
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:23,240
What did you say?

173
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:25,880
Qianjin

174
00:13:26,440 --> 00:13:27,640
What are you going to do?

175
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:33,440
Lin Qianjin

176
00:13:34,520 --> 00:13:35,640
The position of City Lord's wife

177
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:37,560
is not something you can just refuse at will.

178
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:39,200
Even if you don't love me,

179
00:13:39,560 --> 00:13:40,440
I will still marry you as

180
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:41,760
my City Lord's wife.

181
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:44,760
You must take on the responsibilities of the City Lord's wife.

182
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:48,440
No.

183
00:13:49,800 --> 00:13:51,760
If Li Yan is gone,

184
00:13:52,760 --> 00:13:54,200
then being the City Lord's wife

185
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,320
means nothing to me.

186
00:13:57,320 --> 00:13:59,880
I just want Li Yan to live well.

187
00:14:00,560 --> 00:14:02,640
Are you going to defy the City Lord's order?

188
00:14:09,880 --> 00:14:11,000
Then, City Lord,

189
00:14:12,640 --> 00:14:14,320
please punish me here and now.

190
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:40,960
Lin Qianjin

191
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,120
has defied the City Lord's order.

192
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:45,080
Exile her to the borderlands.

193
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:46,640
She is to depart immediately.

194
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:48,440
From this day forward,

195
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:51,320
she is forbidden from setting foot in Nanling City.

196
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:57,160
Go.

197
00:14:58,520 --> 00:14:59,320
Nanling City

198
00:15:00,400 --> 00:15:01,440
can no longer tolerate you.

199
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:04,920
Thank you, City Lord, for granting my wish.
